Emerald Radiance Grand Haaram - A Timeless Legacy

₹82,190

Description

This Grand Haaram is a heirloom-worthy piece, embodying the rich cultural heritage of South India. The combination of precious gemstones and expert craftsmanship ensures lasting beauty and value. The intricate design and traditional motifs make it a truly unique and unforgettable statement piece.

Materials

  • 22K Yellow Gold (సువర్ణం)
  • Exquisite Emeralds (పచ్చలు) with excellent clarity
  • brilliant-cut Diamonds (వజ్రాలు)
  • and lustrous South Sea Pearls (ముత్యాలు). Crafted with traditional Hyderabadi Polish for a lasting shine.

Features

This majestic Haaram showcases a floral motif arrangement adorned with emeralds and diamonds, exuding regal charm. The intricate diamond work is meticulously handcrafted. Delicate pearl droplets add a touch of grace. The pendant features a larger emerald center stone and is framed by a complex filigree design that blends tradition with contemporary aesthetics.
